        KV -->|"3. Decode 拉取 KV"| Decode["Decode 实例群<br/>大并发 · 访存优化"]
        Decode -->|"4. 逐 token 输出"| Client
    end

    style 一体化 fill:#2a1a1a,stroke:#d4a574,stroke-width:1px
    style PD分离 fill:#1a2a1a,stroke:#d4a574,stroke-width:1px
